---
title: Italian-Inspired Bison Burgers with Caramelized Onions and Parmesan Potato Wedges
description: Get your napkins ready – this is one seriously juicy burger! We've loaded it with flavour, from the caramelized onions to the Italian mayo and Parmesan potato wedges,  every bite takes you to your happy place.
